0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">30</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">分钟。</span></p><p style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 宋体;font-size: 12px;white-space: normal;line-height: 29px;text-indent: 32px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">（</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">3</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">）天津西站（火车）</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">——</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">天津工业大学</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">:</span></p><p style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 宋体;font-size: 12px;white-space: normal;line-height: 29px;text-indent: 32px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">可乘坐天津地铁六号线再换乘地铁三号线。从天津西站地铁站乘坐地铁六号线（开往南翠屏方向）至</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">“</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">红旗南路站</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">”</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">，换乘地铁三号线（开往南站方向）到大学城地铁站，下车即到。大约用时</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">45</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">分钟。</span></p><p style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 宋体;font-size: 12px;white-space: normal;line-height: 29px;text-indent: 32px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">（</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">4</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">）天津南站（火车）</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">——</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">天津工业大学：</span></p><p style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 宋体;font-size: 12px;white-space: normal;line-height: 29px;text-indent: 32px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">可乘坐天津地铁三号线（开往小淀方向），从天津南站地铁站到大学城地铁站，下车即到。大约用时</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">15</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">分钟。</span></p><p style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 宋体;font-size: 12px;white-space: normal;line-height: 29px;text-indent: 32px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">（</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">5</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">）天津滨海国际机场</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">——</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">天津工业大学：</span></p><p style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 宋体;font-size: 12px;white-space: normal;line-height: 29px;text-indent: 32px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">可乘坐天津地铁二号线再换乘地铁三号线。从天津滨海国际机场地铁站乘坐地铁二号线（开往曹庄方向）至</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">“</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">天津站</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">”</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">，换乘天津地铁三号线（开往南站方向）到大学城地铁站。大约用时</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">1.5</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">小时。</span></p><p style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 宋体;font-size: 12px;white-space: normal;line-height: 29px\"><strong style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">十、其它说明</span></strong><strong style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px\"></strong></p><p style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 宋体;font-size: 12px;white-space: normal;line-height: 29px;text-indent: 32px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">为保证夏令营活动的质量，我们将限制夏令营营员人数，故不能满足所有对本夏令营感兴趣的同学申请，但不影响未被录取者继续报考本校研究生。其它信息可咨询实验室，联系方式等均可参见实验室网站：</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px\"><a href=\"http://membrane.tjpu.edu.cn/\" style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(51, 51, 51)\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px\">membrane.tjpu.edu.cn</span></a></span></p><p style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 宋体;font-size: 12px;white-space: normal;line-height: 29px;text-indent: 32px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">请同学注意出行安全，在夏令营期间医疗费用及因个人原因导致的意外事故费用，由学员本人及派出单位承担。</span></p><p style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 宋体;font-size: 12px;white-space: normal;line-height: 29px;text-indent: 32px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">有问题可直接与重点实验室田磊老师联系（</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">13902134013</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">；</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">022-83955297</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">）。</span></p><p style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 宋体;font-size: 12px;white-space: normal;text-align: right;line-height: 29px;text-indent: 32px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 宋体;font-size: 12px;white-space: normal;text-align: right;line-height: 29px;text-indent: 32px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">天津工业大学研究生院</span></p><p style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 宋体;font-size: 12px;white-space: normal;text-align: right;line-height: 29px;text-indent: 32px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">分离膜与膜过程国家重点实验室</span></p><p style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;color: rgb(68, 68, 68);font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, 宋体;font-size: 12px;white-space: normal;text-align: right;line-height: 29px;text-indent: 32px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">2017</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">年</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">6</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">月</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, serif;font-size: 16px\">2</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;border: 0px;font-family: 宋体;font-size: 16px\">日</span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n							</p>', null, '2018-10-17 10:35:33', '2017-08-04 11:39:09', null, '5f8f4f86-602a-4d0c-b02c-abb74b9f3eaf', '1539743733813.png');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('7a0c1899-988b-4495-8c84-845dc52e53f2', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', '9ad9abdb-78c5-4ebd-8242-824cd0f7640c', null, null, 'How can Chinese students benefit from the undergraduate transfer policy in the United States?', 'Tianjin International Education Exchange Service Center (hereinafter referred to as the ', '<p>							</p><p><br/></p><p>Tianjin International Education Exchange Service Center (hereinafter referred to as the &quot;center&quot;) is the institution directly under the Tianjin Municipal Education Commission. Its predecessor was the Tianjin overseas students service center established in 1993, and in 2001 it became more and more important</p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n							</p>', null, '2018-10-17 10:36:16', '2017-09-06 11:11:40', null, 'e67a2792-3819-41f9-92d3-bfa5f8e79d70', '1539743776712.jfif');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('91575132-3154-4d4b-a437-25884d080680', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', '8cf0b169-ec1c-4edc-a5f0-d6fd7afde4cf', null, null, '留学行前安全培训要点分享', '', '<p>							</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;一、安全防范意识植入脑中最为重要，时时处处记得警醒自已。国内外安全环境和文化与国内的异同，适应国外留学环境并自觉抵制不良文化及诱惑。君子不立危墙之下。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;二、建立安全沟通机制和个人安全防范准备。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、与国内亲人或境外留学好友定时联系确认安全，有异常情况可以第一时间发现并处置。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、随身携带简便防身器械如防狼喷剂、电棒等。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;三、各种环境情况下的防范及处置。首先一定要头脑冷静，切忌自乱阵脚。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、进入各种场所养成习惯先观察消防或逃生通道以及相邻区域有无潜在不安全因素；</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、居室安全防范，窗台摆放物品等。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3、开车或掏钥匙进住所时一定要先观察周边。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4、开门时的正确方式。5、摆脱尾随。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;四、面对徒手歹徒如何应对。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、抓住手腕手臂部位时，迅速用未受控制的手握拳挥击对方太阳穴；</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、双手被控制时，迅速踢击对方裆部或小腿迎面骨；</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3、正面搂抱时视情双拳相向挥击对方耳部、用膝盖撞击对方裆部或脚跺对方大脚趾；</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4、后面搂抱时重心前倾并用力跺对方脚趾。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;五、面对持刀歹徒如何应对。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1、放弃空手夺刃幻想。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2、侧闪躲避。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3、利用随身物品挥击闪躲。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;4、衣物缠臂格挡。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;5、利用周围物品抵挡。目的都是避免刺伤并争取逃跑时间尽快逃离。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;六、偶遇暴恐袭击等突发状况时的紧急避险应对。</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n							</p>', null, '2018-10-17 10:38:35', '2017-08-07 09:25:41', null, '5f8f4f86-602a-4d0c-b02c-abb74b9f3eaf', '1539743915451.jpg');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('92febd28-4e9c-47c9-b311-3cbe2793ee5b', '8f0b9be9-a527-4df0-8768-a22cd4cb0b28', '9ad9abdb-78c5-4ebd-1242-824cd0f7640c', null, null, '国际组织实习项目选派管理办法', '', '<h1 style=\";margin-bottom:0;text-align:center;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:22px;font-family:&#39;Helvetica&#39;,sans-serif;color:black;background:white\">国际组织实习项目选派管理办法</span></h1><p><br/></p>', null, '2018-12-02 16:05:24', '2018-12-02 16:05:24', null, '5f8f4f86-602a-4d0c-b02c-abb74b9f3eaf', null);
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('9436daf7-b095-4de9-86df-b2e286d7213b', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', '799c1cdb-8b0b-4c4d-a210-cd7fcb51cd21', null, null, '世界宜居之选', '', '<p>							</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">据英国经济学人资讯社全球宜居城市调查显示，天津是中国大陆最宜居城市之一。天津还获选中国最具幸福感城市。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n							</p>', null, '2018-10-17 10:39:41', '2017-12-04 10:19:50', null, '5f8f4f86-602a-4d0c-b02c-abb74b9f3eaf', '1539743981484.jpg');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('94dc255f-ce03-44f3-87f1-cbfe4b0c0bb2', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', '9ad9abdb-78c5-4ebd-8242-824cd0f7640c', null, null, '2017 Jintai college students', 'The news (correspondent Wang Guodong) in August 3rd, 2017 Tianjin Taiwan College Students ', '<p>							</p><p><br/></p><p>The news (correspondent Wang Guodong) in August 3rd, 2017 Tianjin Taiwan College Students &quot;Haihe River feeling&quot; summer camp opening ceremony held in Tianjin University.</p><p>The summer camp is hosted by the civil Exchange Promotion Association on both sides of the Tianjin city and the union of China&#39;s unified Taiwan, Tianjin University. Tianjin affairs office director Liu Jianying attended the opening ceremony and for the campers on behalf of the flag, vice president of Tianjin University Hu Wenping, Deputy Secretary General of Taiwan China unity alliance long, Taipei branch executive Han Yanming attended the opening ceremony. Tianjin City, Taiwan Affairs Office of Taiwan Affairs Office of Tianjin University and science department of Hong Kong and Macao related teachers attended the ceremony.</p><p>The opening ceremony, Hu Wenping on behalf of Tianjin University students in Taiwan and a warm welcome, and thank you for a long time on the day of the Taiwan Affairs Office of Tianjin city on Taiwan&#39;s support. Hu Wenping introduced to the teachers and students in Taiwan in detail the achievements made in the history of school building, the characteristics of school running and the training of talents in Tianjin University. He hopes that students from both sides of the Taiwan Straits will learn from each other, enhance their feelings and make common progress in the 7 day activities.</p><p>In his speech, Han Yanming expressed his sincere thanks to the Tianjin University for the support of the &quot;Haihe love&quot; summer camp. Han Yanming said that young people are the hope of the nation and the future of the motherland. We should constantly create conditions to enhance communication and communication between the young people on both sides of the Straits. The successful hosting of the &quot;Haihe love&quot; summer camp has built a bridge of communication for the students of jimtai, and has achieved good results. He hopes that the young people on both sides of the Taiwan Straits can join hands to work together for the happiness of their compatriots on both sides of the Straits and contribute to the development of the society.</p><p>From the Tianjin University and the Taiwan student representatives made a statement, said to the same origin of the Chinese culture as a link, mutual respect, enhance mutual exchanges, promote feelings, to contribute to the development of cross-strait peace together.</p><p>After the opening ceremony, all campers jointly visited the Tianjin University Feng Jicai Institute of literature and art, and discussion with Mr. Feng Jicai. Mr. Feng Jicai warmly welcomed the arrival of young students. He introduced the main contents and achievements of the academy to students. Feng Jicai&#39;s message to students on both sides to enhance the identity of the Chinese culture, read more exchanges to think, to contribute to the inheritance and development of Chinese civilization.</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n							</p>', null, '2018-10-17 10:42:00', '2017-12-07 09:17:32', null, 'e67a2792-3819-41f9-92d3-bfa5f8e79d70', '1539744120808.jfif');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('984cfd80-eefd-4826-a0fb-b3bfedf45aa6', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', '9ad9abdb-78c5-4ebd-8242-824cd0f7640c', null, null, '中国留学生如何受益于美国本科转学政策', '天津市国际教育交流服务中心（以下简称“中心”）', '<p>							</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(251, 251, 251);\">天津市国际教育交流服务中心（以下简称“中心”）是天津市教育委员会直属事业单位，其前身为1993年成立的天津市留学人员服务中心，2001年更为</span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n							</p>', null, '2018-10-17 10:43:08', '2017-07-21 10:26:07', null, '5f8f4f86-602a-4d0c-b02c-abb74b9f3eaf', '1539744188577.jpg');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('9f8946fa-5266-4f90-9043-44af3232e0f3', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', '799c1cdb-8b0b-4c4d-a210-cd7fcb51cd25', null, null, '关于我们', '留学天津的创建是为了实现来华留学生通过网络系统平台在天津申请学校及奖学金服务，同时为留学生提供留学生活的相关信息。来华留学生可以通过系统平台知道什么学校适合自己，如何申请这些学校。因此，我们建立了这样一个平台，旨在帮助来华留学生做到这一点。     但合理的学习计划仅仅是个开始。来华留学生需要思考未来的职业计划。近年来，来华留学生人数连年攀升，中国正逐渐成为有竞争力的留学大国。面对未来，以“科学发展观”为指导思想，加强留学生职业生涯规范教育成为来华留学工作的重要组成部分。', '<p>							</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 留学天津的创建是为了实现来华留学生通过网络系统平台在天津申请学校及奖学金服务，同时为留学生提供留学生活的相关信息。来华留学生可以通过系统平台知道什么学校适合自己，如何申请这些学校。因此，我们建立了这样一个平台，旨在帮助来华留学生做到这一点。<br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; 但合理的学习计划仅仅是个开始。来华留学生需要思考未来的职业计划。近年来，来华留学生人数连年攀升，中国正逐渐成为有竞争力的留学大国。面对未来，以“科学发展观”为指导思想，加强留学生职业生涯规范教育成为来华留学工作的重要组成部分。</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n							</p>', null, '2018-10-17 10:44:42', '2017-07-21 09:38:47', null, '5f8f4f86-602a-4d0c-b02c-abb74b9f3eaf', '1539744282728.jfif');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('9ff18ca5-102d-4d5b-80d6-a3508bdfccd7', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', '799c1cdb-8b0b-4c4d-a210-cd7fcb51cd23', null, null, '​天津（中华人民共和国直辖市）', '天津，简称津，中华人民共和国直辖市、国家中心城市、超大城市、环渤海地区经济中心、首批沿海开放城市，全国先进制造研发基地、北方国际航运核心区、金融创新运营示范区、改革开放先行区。    天津自古因漕运而兴起，明永乐二年十一月二十一日（1404年12月23日）正式筑城，是中国古代唯一有确切建城时间记录的城市。历经600多年，造就了天津中西合璧、古今兼容的独特城市风貌。', '<p>							</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 天津，简称津，中华人民共和国直辖市、国家中心城市、超大城市、 环渤海地区经济中心、首批沿海开放城市，全国先进制造研发基地、北方国际航运核心区、金融创新运营示范区、改革开放先行区。<br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 天津自古因漕运而兴起，明永乐二年十一月二十一日（1404年12月23日）正式筑城，是中国古代唯一有确切建城时间记录的城市。历经600多年，造就了天津中西合璧、古今兼容的独特城市风貌。</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 天津位于华北平原海河五大支流汇流处，东临渤海，北依燕山，海河在城中蜿蜒而过，海河是天津的母亲河。天津滨海新区被誉为“中国经济第三增长极”。天津是夏季达沃斯论坛常驻举办城市。</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2014年12月12日，位于天津市滨海新区的中国（天津）自由贸易试验区正式获得国家批准设立。2015年4月21日，中国(天津)自由贸易试验区正式挂牌。中国（天津）自由贸易试验区为中国北方第一个自贸区。</p><p><br/></p><p><strong>政治</strong></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 天津市人民代表大会及其常务委员会是天津市的国家权力机关。选民直接选举区、县人民代表，代表大会每届任期5年。</p><p><strong>经济</strong></p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1860年天津成为通商口岸以后，西方多国在天津设立租界，天津成为中国开放的前沿和近代中国“洋务”运动的基地。由天津开始的军事近代化，以及铁路、电报、电话、邮政、采矿、近代教育、司法等方面建设，均开中国之先河，创造了近代中国100个第一。天津自从清末民初时期已是中国经济最发达的城市之一，近现代工商、金融业兴盛繁荣。</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 自2005年天津滨海新区纳入国家十一五规划和国家发展战略，并批准滨海新区为国家综合配套改革试验区。2006年3月22日，国务院常务会议将天津完整定位为“环渤海地区经济中心，国际港口城市，北方经济中心，生态城市”，并将“推进滨海新区开发开放”纳入十一五规划和国家战略，设立为国家综合配套改革试验区。</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2008年起，世界经济论坛新领军者年会开始落户天津举办，夏季达沃斯论坛的永久会址位于天津北塘国际会议中心。至2014年8月，世界500强跨国公司已有156家在天津落地生根，投资项目共465个。2014年12月12日，中国（天津）自由贸易试验区获得批准。同年12月28日，经国务院正式批准设立试验区总面积为119.9平方公里。&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2016年，天津生产总值17885.39亿元，按可比价格计算，比上年增长9.0%。其中，第一产业增加值220.22亿元，增长3.0%；第二产业增加值8003.87亿元，增长8.0%；第三产业增加值9661.30亿元，增长10.0%。三次产业结构为1.2:44.8:54.0。一般公共预算收入2723.46亿元，增长10.0%。其中，税收收入1624.18亿元，增长12.1%，比上年提高5.9个百分点，占一般公共预算收入的59.6%。从主体税种看，增值税455.80亿元，增长36.4%；企业所得税278.42亿元，增长7.1%；个人所得税96.78亿元，增长18.4%。</p><p><br/></p><p><strong>文化</strong></p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 天津话是北方方言中的一种，流行于天津及其周边地区，特指以天津老城为中心的一个尖朝南，底朝北的三角形“天津方言岛”内人们所说的方言。</p><p><strong>宗教</strong><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 截至2015年，天津有五种宗教得到政府承认：佛教、道教、伊斯兰教、天主教和基督新教。全市教徒共26.7万人，宗教职业人员近200人。1979年以来共恢复开放宗教活动场所79处，其中佛教的大悲院被列为汉族地区佛教全国重点寺院，天主教的望海楼天主堂被列为中国重点文物保护单位，被列为天津市文物保护单位的有天主教天津教区的主教座堂西开教堂、伊斯兰教的清真大寺、基督教安里甘教堂以及道教的天津天后宫和玉皇阁。</p><p><strong>饮食</strong><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;天津饮食文化享誉中国，这里不仅有传统的地方小吃，更拥有中国各地的美味佳肴。据史料记载，清代（公元1644—1911年）第四位皇帝 —— 乾隆皇帝非常喜欢天津的美食料理，以至于奖赏他的津门厨师一件代表无上荣耀的黄马褂并任命他为正四品官员。在天津，你可以看见无数特色美食街和风味餐厅，用美食来满足你的味蕾。<br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;天津人的饮食习俗的形成不仅同天津的地理环境有密切的关系，也受历史传承、居民变化、文化交流的深刻影响。历史上的天津，因为河多、湾多，加上湖、淀、塘等，水域宽阔，距海又近，故水产品极为丰富，品种也多。海河之中，鱼虾蟹蚌，应有尽有。天津人喜食海鲜、河鲜，就是由这得天独厚的优越条件养成的。</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 天津人有一句俗语：“当当吃海货，不算不会过。”津菜借助天津的物产，历经几百年的发展，逐步完善成一个涵盖汉民菜、清真菜、家乡地方特色菜和民间风味小吃的体系。</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">津门“三绝”</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">狗不理包子</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; “狗不理”包子是天津地方传统风味食品，始创于公元1858 年清朝咸丰年间，历经一百五十多年的狗不理包子，如今也有了官方英文的名字“Go Believe”。它的知名度可谓“没吃过狗不理，就不算到过天津”。</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">桂发祥十八街麻花</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 桂发祥十八街麻花起源于公元1927 年，麻花店坐落于河西区十八街并由此而得名。麻花采用优质的面粉过油炸制而成。在中国，十八街麻花是非常棒的礼物，因为它可以保存三个月之久，所以你可以带一些这种酥脆的特产回家并与家人分享。</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">耳朵眼炸糕</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 炸糕是天津当地一种甜味小吃，不要因为它有一个奇怪名字，而使你疏远这种黏米糕点。耳朵眼炸糕有百余年历史，创始人叫刘万春，因摊位在红桥区耳朵眼胡同而得名。这种糕点由发酵的糯米团制成，表皮金黄而酥脆，豆沙馅儿甜蜜而美味，耳朵眼炸糕一定会满足喜爱甜食的你。</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p><strong>舌尖上的盛宴——尽在天津卫</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">去壳后果实松软香甜，为小吃珍品</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">天津特产糖炒栗子醇香味美，可搭配各种卤菜</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">天津特色面食天津捞面</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">用山楂串成，酥脆亮香</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">天津特色小吃冰糖葫芦</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">香甜滑爽, 极为可口</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">天津特色小吃茶汤</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">用热油炸熟，外脆里香</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">天津特色早点卷圈</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">鲜咸爽口，卤浓而不腻，锅巴嚼劲十足</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">天津特色早点锅巴菜</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">色香味美，营养丰富</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">天津特色早点煎饼馃子</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: sinmsun; line-height: 26px;\">天津：五大国家战略叠加区</strong></p><p>　　2015年，天津市GDP总量居全国第五，仅次于北上广深。这一年，对天津的意义非同凡响，滨海新区开发开放、京津冀协同发展、“一带一路”、自贸区、国家自主创新示范区，五大国家发展战略同时叠加，全国只此一家。</p><p>　　在南开大学滨海开发研究院院长助理薄文广看来，天津最大的优势，是紧靠北京的区域优势，“从区域平衡角度，或者区域协同发展角度，天津是一个非常重要的支点。”</p><p>　　尽管是“灯下黑”，但天津在行政层级上是直辖市，也是北方特殊的交通、港口、物流枢纽，可以辐射环渤海乃至三北地区。</p><p>　　天津和其它城市相比，最大的优势是人口流入量非常大，近年来平均每年增加近50万人。</p><p>　　原因主要有两个：一是天津自身的大项目、大工程，吸引大量人才；二是北京限制人口规模导致的外溢效应。</p><p>　　天津的高速增长，依靠的是国家的政策红利带来的大批重点工业项目。自滨海新区成为国家战略以来，其累计的固定资产投资达到数万亿。滨海新区因大飞机等领军的高端重工业竞争力很强，在未来也具有广阔的想象空间。</p><p>　　获批自贸区成为创新的绝佳契机。依托自贸区这个支点，天津吸引了更多资金和人才，未来更要建立与国际贸易投资规则相适应的体制机制，建设制度创新新高地、转型升级新引擎。</p><p>　　金融领域中，天津的融资租赁一直领跑全国。如果说北京是中国金融的决策中心，上海是中国金融的交易中心，深圳是中国金融的市场中心，天津则是产业金融中心。</p><p>　　天津在“十三五”规划纲要中强调，要加快国家租赁创新示范区建设。与自贸区对应的“金改30条”后，天津的融资租赁业务更是飞速发展，租赁飞机占到全国的90%，租赁船舶占到全国的80%。</p><p>　　得益于京津冀协同发展规划，未来京津之间将有5条快速铁路或高铁。目前天津到北京正在考虑修建新的城际铁路，该铁路将连接北京新机场。接下来，产业转移的带动效应也将呈现。</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n							</p>', null, '2018-10-17 10:45:42', '2017-06-29 17:18:49', null, '5f8f4f86-602a-4d0c-b02c-abb74b9f3eaf', '1539744342480.jpg');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('a36977ae-a3d5-4ca5-9034-6653b7fa6503', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', '799c1cdb-8b0b-4c4d-a210-cd7fcb51cd21', null, null, '中国海归人才需求趋势', '', '<p>							</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 18.75pt; text-indent: 24pt; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">中国是变化最快的国家，这种变化，吸引着每年数十万海归像候鸟一样进行着人类有史以来最长距离的迁徙。然而出国的人越多，海归也越多。中国海归正在经历一个从量变到质变的阵痛。越来越多的海待，让人不禁问道：</span>“<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 18.75pt; text-indent: 24pt; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">究竟是留学留错了，还是海归归错了？</span>”<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 18.75pt; text-indent: 18pt;\">其实留学的价值并没有随着时代的变迁而减少，海归也是大势所趋。真正错的是留学心态，当多数家长还在留学前忖度孩子选择金融还是管理等热门专业时，有谁想过国家未来的人才需求。学什么专业的海归才能大有前途。在研究了一遍全国各地海归人才引进项目后，发现金融、管理等人文社科类专业并非发展的首要稀缺人才。出现频率最多的专业关键词前三位为：机械装备制造，新材料和生物科技。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">1</strong></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">、四类海归人才将走俏中国</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">今年，我国将出台《</span>2015-2017<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">留学工作行动计划》，加大力度培养的五类人才：尖端人才、国际组织人才、非通用语种人才、来华青年杰出人才、国别和区域研究人才。除</span>“<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">来华青年杰出人才</span>”<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">是针对外国人，其余都与海归群体有直接关系。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">尖端人才属于技术类创造性人才。清华大学技术创新研究中心去年发布的《国家创新蓝皮书》指出，我国研发人员人均产出效率远落后于发达国家。以</span>IT<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">服务行业为例，我国</span>IT<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">高附加值的跨国服务收入只占总收入的</span>10%<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">，而印度达</span>75%<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">随着中国的崛起，中国的国际地位也不断提升。国际舞台上，国际组织人才起关键作用。在海归群体中，一批外语能力强，通晓专业知识（如国际法、国际金融）的佼佼者便是补充人才库的重要来源。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">在</span>2014<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">年年底召开的全国留学工作会议上，国家对于非通用语人才的需求被屡次提及。目前和中国建交的</span>175<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">个国家中，通用语种约</span>95<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">种，而内地仅能开设</span>54<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">种语言课程；</span>“<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">一带一路</span>”<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">战略涉及官方语言</span>40<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">余种，而目前内地仅能教授</span>20<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">几种。小语种留学生未来进入大学授课或成为国际会议翻译的几率要远大于只会英语的留学生。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">国别和区域研究人才是《</span>2015-2017<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">留学工作行动计划》中特别提出的一类特殊人才。有海外学习经历，对国外政治、经济、文化都十分了解的人士将有机会加入国家智库。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">2</strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">、中西部地区对海归人才需求强烈</span></strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">根据《中国留学生回国就业蓝皮书</span>2014<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">》，</span>57.94%<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">的海归将就业城市瞄准北上广深，造成人才扎堆。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">而随着我国沿海城市的人才市场日趋饱和，发展潜力较大的中西部地区将成为海归的理性选择。中西部对有国际视野的优秀海归人才十分渴求，一些地区更是对某些专业的海归情有独钟。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">3</strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">、什么专业的海归大有前途</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">近年来海归与国内大学毕业生薪酬的差距日益缩小，原因何在？海归专业同质化是一大原因。《中国留学回国就业蓝皮书</span>2014<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">》显示，工商管理和应用经济学两个学科的海归竟占到海归总人数的</span>45.75%<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">家长和学生在做留学规划时，不妨做个逆向推导，借助了解未来</span>5-10<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">年国家对人才的需求，再结合学生的特长和兴趣，做好职业规划，从而为选择留学目的国、学校、专业规划出明确的方向。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\">“<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">千人计划</span>”<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">、</span>“<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">长江学者奖励计划</span>”<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">、</span>“<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">百人计划</span>”<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">从中央到地方层面的一系列引才政策都能为准留学生做好学业规划、职业规划提供参考。最后，到底学什么专业的海归大有前途？</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">a</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">、海外人才引进计划（西北）</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">宁夏百人计划、青海高科技产业开发区、陕西百人计划、甘肃省</span>“<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">高层人才科技创新创业扶持行动</span>”<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">等。热门领域</span>:<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">农产品精深加工、民族和社会研究、现代交通运输、航空航天、生物医药。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">b</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">、海外人才引进计划（西南）</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">四川百人计划、云南百名海外高层次人才引进计划、贵州省高层次人才引进工程、重庆千名优秀人才引进计划等。热门领域：商贸物流、工程技术、国际经济与贸易、民族民间文化特色优势产业、生态和城镇化建设。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">c</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">、海外人才引进计划（华南）</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">深圳</span>“<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">孔雀计划</span>”<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">。热门领域：新能源、互联网、文化创意、新材料</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">d</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">、海外人才引进计划（华北）</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">北京海外人才聚集工程、天津千人计划、河北百人计划等。热门领域</span>“<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">工程技术、现代物流、国际经济法、社会科学</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">e</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">、海外人才引进计划（东北）</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">吉林省引进高层次人才创新创业计划等。热门领域：石油化工、农产品加工、医药、冶金建材、新材料。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">f</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">、海外人才引进计划（华东）</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">上海海外高层次人才集聚工程、厦门市高层次人才引进双百计划、江西赣番英才</span>555<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">工程等。热门领域：通讯、文化创意、新材料技术、生态牧业、信息服务。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 18.75pt;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">g</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">、海外人才引进计划（华中）</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">武汉东湖</span>“3551”<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">人才计划、湖南百人洛阳市海外高层次引进</span>1211<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">工程等。热门领域：环境保护、生物医药产业、智能装备制造产业、光电子信息产业。</span></p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n							</p>', null, '2018-10-17 10:46:53', '2017-12-04 10:52:48', null, '5f8f4f86-602a-4d0c-b02c-abb74b9f3eaf', '1539744413520.jfif');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('a8399cb9-704a-4bbb-970b-3535a500e233', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', '799c1cdb-8b0b-4c4d-a210-cd7fcb51cd20', null, null, '天津教育', '天津教育', '<p>							</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">天津是我国近代教育的发祥地之一。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">始建于1904 年的天津南开中学先后走出了新中国的两任总理：周恩来总理和温家宝总理。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://192.168.30.116/Js/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170629/1498725066660021346.png\" title=\"1498725066660021346.png\" alt=\"blob.png\"/>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">周恩来</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">中华人民共和国首任总理</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">1913 年8 月至1917 年6 月在南开中学学习</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">1. 天津教育概况</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">天津市共有各级各类学校2975所，在校生183.9 万人，专任教师13 万人。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">学前教育：幼儿园1461 所，在园幼儿22.9 万人，专任教师1.1万人，学前三年入园率达到95%。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">义务教育：小学843 所，在校生53.2 万人，专任教师3.8 万人；初中317 所，在校生25.7 万人，专任教师2.6 万人。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">普通高中：普通高中202 所，在校生18.1 万人，专任教师1.5 万人。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">中职教育：中职学校97 所，在校生11.8 万人，专任教师8880 人。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"~/../Js/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170711/1499757182841098082.png\" title=\"1499757182841098082.png\" alt=\"blob.png\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">高等教育：普通高校55 所（含10所独立学院）。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">其中本科院校29 所、高职学院26所，在校生52.2 万人，专任教师3 万人。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://192.168.30.116/Js/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170629/1498725230648073393.png\" title=\"1498725230648073393.png\" alt=\"blob.png\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">2. 教育体系</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">天津拥有从学前至高等教育的完整教育体系。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">2.1 小学教育</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">• 小学教育为6 年制，入学年龄为7 岁。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">2.2 中等教育</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">• 初中教育为3 年制；</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">• 高中教育为3 年制；</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">• 中等职业教育为3 年制。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">备注：小学与初中教育为义务教育阶段。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">2.3 高等教育</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">• 职业教育：一般为三年，授予高等教育</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">文凭。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">• 大学教育：</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">本科一般为4 年，授予学士学位；</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">硕士研究生一般为2 年，授予硕士学位；</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">博士研究生一般为3~4 年，授予博士学位。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://192.168.30.116/Js/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20170629/1498725467487029515.png\" title=\"1498725467487029515.png\" alt=\"blob.png\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">3. 学期</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">一个学年由两个学期组成，第一个学期从9 月初到翌年1 月中旬，第二学期从2 月底到6 月底。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">寒假从1 月中旬到2 月底，暑假从6 月底到9 月初。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">4. 奖学金</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">• 天津市共有13 所高等院校为接受中国政府奖学金高校。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">• 天津市教育委员会设立天津市高校外国留学生奖学金项目，为天津市高等院校的优秀国际学生提供奖学金资助。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">天津市高校外国留学生奖学金标准及资助期限</span></p><table><tbody><tr class=\"firstRow\"><td width=\"137\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(141, 179, 226);\">学生类别</td><td width=\"137\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(141, 179, 226);\">专业学习年限</td><td width=\"137\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(141, 179, 226);\">奖学金限期</td><td width=\"137\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(141, 179, 226);\">奖学金标准</td></tr><tr><td width=\"137\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(198, 217, 240);\">本科生</td><td width=\"137\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(216, 216, 216);\">4~5 年</td><td width=\"137\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(216, 216, 216);\">4~5 年</td><td width=\"137\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(216, 216, 216);\">20000 元/ 人年</td></tr><tr><td width=\"137\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(198, 217, 240);\">硕士研究生</td><td width=\"137\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(216, 216, 216);\">2~3 年</td><td width=\"137\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(216, 216, 216);\">2~3 年</td><td width=\"137\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(216, 216, 216);\">30000 元/ 人年</td></tr><tr><td width=\"137\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(198, 217, 240);\">博士研究生</td><td width=\"137\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(216, 216, 216);\">3 年</td><td width=\"137\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(216, 216, 216);\">3 年</td><td width=\"137\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(216, 216, 216);\">40000 元/ 人年</td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">天津市高校外国留学生奖学金申请途径和申请时间</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">1. 根据天津市政府、天津市教委与外国省州政府、教育管理部门或国际组织、学校达成的协议或计划，通过所在国负责留学生派遣的政府部门、相关机构向天津市高等学校提出申请；</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">2. 可通过中国驻外使、领馆向天津市高等学校提出申请；</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">3. 可直接向天津市高等学校提出申请；</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">4. 申请时间为每年1 月至6 月初。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">5. 汉语水平考试</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">HSK 是一项国际汉语能力标准化考试，重点考查汉语非第一语言的考生在生活、学习和工</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">作中运用汉语进行交际的能力。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">• 考试结构： HSK 包括HSK 一级、HSK 二级、HSK 三级、HSK 四级、HSK 五级和HSK 六级。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">• 考试形式：1. 纸笔考试；2. 网络考试（网络考试是基于互联网和计算机实施的考试，考</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">试内容、标准和效力与纸笔考试相同。汉语网络考试支持在线缴费和在线模拟）。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">• 考试用途：HSK 已成为留学中国的通行证、申请来华留学奖学金的必备条件和学校教学</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">评估的重要手段，并被越来越多国家的政府部门和跨国企业作为员工招聘、提薪和晋升的</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">重要依据。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">• 考试报名与成绩报告：HSK 成绩是汉语能力的权威证明，考生可在考试结束一个月后登</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">录汉语考试服务网www.chinesetest.cn 查询成绩，并于成绩公布一个月内联系参加考试</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">的考点获取由孔子学院总部/ 国家汉办颁发的HSK 成绩报告。</p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">• 天津市各高等院校为国际学生提供HSK 课程。</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n							</p>', null, '2018-10-17 10:48:03', '2017-07-11 15:13:12', null, '5f8f4f86-602a-4d0c-b02c-abb74b9f3eaf', '1539744483097.jfif');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('b29083c4-15b5-4a74-a328-9fa65b8bed82', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', '3a5a03ae-418d-40b0-8d51-f943c34d76c0', null, null, '天津城市中心略图', '', '', null, '2018-10-17 10:48:52', '2017-12-03 17:17:37', null, '5f8f4f86-602a-4d0c-b02c-abb74b9f3eaf', '1539744532896.jpg');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('b2eb107f-b505-49b8-8559-dfb6ff0be600', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', '799c1cdb-8b0b-4c4d-a210-cd7fcb51cd21', null, null, '国际多元文化', '', '<p>							</p><p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;天津是最早与西方近代文明接触的中国城市之一。自1860 年被辟为对外通商口岸，天津成为中国北方开放的前沿城市。中西文化的碰撞与交融相生，涵养了天津的开放思维、现代意识和多元文化包容力。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 天津是一座充满活力、极具开放性和包容性的城市，与国内外众多城市和地区保持着密切而活跃的交流与合作。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 天津自1973 年与日本神户市建立友好城市以来，逐步加强国际交流。目前，天津与五大洲45 个国家的70 余个地区建立多种形式友好交流与合作关系。随着改革开放的进一步发展，天津市已逐渐成为举世瞩目的国际港口城市。</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n							</p>', null, '2018-10-17 10:50:42', '2017-12-04 10:20:11', null, '5f8f4f86-602a-4d0c-b02c-abb74b9f3eaf', '1539744642193.jpg');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('b66233ca-297b-4068-a75b-0cbaa7469b71', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', 'c896bf9c-3e2f-4ee0-ab7b-05052e1cd191', null, null, '货币知识', '', '<p>							</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;第五套人民币共6种面额：100元、50元、20元、<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/10%E5%85%83\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">10元</a>、5元、1元。第五套人民币根据市场流通中低面额主币实际起大量承担找零角色的状况，增加了20元面额，取消了2元面额，使面额结构更加合理。第五套人民币采取“一次公布，分次<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%8F%91%E8%A1%8C/29820\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">发行</a>”的方式。1999年10月1日，首先发行100元纸币；2000年10月16日发行20元纸币、1元和1角硬币；2001年9月1日，发行50元、10元纸币；2002年11月18日，发行5元纸币、5角硬币；2004年7月30日，发行1元纸币。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://tmec.demo.raynetwork.net/Js/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20171130/1512014730945083351.png\" title=\"1512014730945083351.png\" alt=\"blob.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://tmec.demo.raynetwork.net/Js/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20171130/1512014843998099903.png\" title=\"1512014843998099903.png\" alt=\"blob.png\" width=\"497\" height=\"369\"/></span></p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n							</p>', null, '2018-10-17 10:52:37', '2017-12-01 09:30:13', null, '5f8f4f86-602a-4d0c-b02c-abb74b9f3eaf', '1539744757006.jpg');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('b73c1bf1-f101-4c3e-a922-98298de9d64c', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', '9ad9abdb-78c5-4ebd-8242-824cd0f7640c', null, null, 'Network security awareness week science and technology day', 'In June 6th, the second session of the national cyber security awareness week into the ', '<p>							</p><p><br/></p><p>In June 6th, the second session of the national cyber security awareness week into the &quot;science and technology&quot;, the Ministry of science and technology, science and Technology Department of China across the country to actively participate in the network safety publicity activities, and network security measures and new technology to the public for the display and interpretation.</p><p>Today, the &quot;network security knowledge forum activities, attract college from the Beijing Association of senior scientists of the older generation of scientists, Beijing Technology and Business University computer science and food science teachers participate in. From the KPMG Business Consulting Co., Chinese senior engineer Jiang Huibai made a speech entitled &quot;the core of the information security concept and composing of the keynote speech, introduced since 2000 emerge in an endless stream of information security incidents, causes and effects of network attack process, the core of information security definition and method for such large-scale information leak prevention and advice to the participants who. He said that the network security incidents generally include IPCS, back door, virus invasion, social engineering and so on. He said the CPC Central Committee in 2014 the establishment of network security and information technology leadership team, is a high-tech look far ahead from a high plane of the strategy, promote the development of national attention to network security, network security will rise to the national level is critical.</p><p>In addition, in the second national network security publicity week &quot;science and technology day&quot; that day, all parts of the country&#39;s science and technology departments also carried out a variety of network security publicity activities. Hebei science and Technology Museum launched the &quot;win in the future&quot; network security education activities for young people. In Hebei province science and Technology Museum, you can see the Hebei Province second session of national network security awareness week publicity posters on the hall prominently, &quot;science and technology of network security knowledge Handbook&quot; placed in the front (the WeChat + networkworldweixin), to visit the youngsters and the public access. In addition, Hebei science and Technology Museum has also been awarded &quot;Hebei science popularization base for network security&quot;&quot;.</p><p>During the publicity week, Hebei will also organize a network of young people&#39;s network security education visits and network security experience activities in Xibaipo patriotism education base. All localities and departments to participate in the activities of science and technology with their own reality, in the &quot;science and technology&quot; to carry out various forms of promotional activities, network security education participation, sharing together to take practical action to promote and practice the.</p><p>In the Internet plus era, the multi-level security defense architecture exist in the network construction of science and technology enterprises, different functions in different levels, namely after the enterprise network is multi-level, enterprises must carry out deep level defense combination of technology and management of the actual situation, by means of science and technology to create a network security environment more clear. (Lu Ningning)</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n							</p>', null, '2018-10-17 10:53:37', '2017-09-06 10:59:28', null, 'e67a2792-3819-41f9-92d3-bfa5f8e79d70', '1539744817240.jfif');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('b9280525-8f0a-41f1-b783-4fff35e0f5b9', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', '0c68a514-51cd-4eba-a57c-50dd0a1e38d4', null, null, '天大人受邀出席天津市国庆招待会', '', '<p>							</p><p><span style=\"\">&nbsp;9月29日下午，天津市庆祝中华人民共和国成立68周年招待会在天津礼堂举行。天津市委书记李鸿忠，市委副书记、市长王东峰，市人大常委会主任肖怀远等市领导同志与中外各界人士代表欢聚一堂，共同庆祝共和国华诞。中国工程院院士、天津大学化工学院教授王静康，天津大学药物科学与技术学院党委书记冯翠玲，以及华北设计总院第一设计研究院院长吴凡松、天地伟业公司董事长戴林等天大校友受邀出席，天大人在国庆招待会共叙友情、互致节日问候。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, arial; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p class=\"Custom_UnionStyle\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"~/../Js/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20171204/1512317957241045411.jpg\"/></span></p><p class=\"Custom_UnionStyle\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"\">　　天大校友吴凡松（右）和戴林（左）受邀出席了招待会</span></p><p class=\"Custom_UnionStyle\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"~/../Js/ueditor/jsp/upload/image/20171204/1512317957631052318.jpg\"/></span></p><p class=\"Custom_UnionStyle\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"\">　　冯翠玲、王静康与中国工程院院士、天津医科大学教授郝希山在招待会上合影</span></p><p class=\"Custom_UnionStyle\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, arial; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"\">　　招待会上，校友戴林汇报了与母校合作的《事件识别光电信息融合感知关键技术》荣获天津市技术发明一等奖的情况。他表示天地伟业要立足“视界为世界”的企业使命和国际化视角，深化与母校的产学研合作，让津产“智”造走向世界，加强自主研发能力，为筑梦天津添砖加瓦，献礼十九大。</span></p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n							</p>', null, '2018-10-17 10:54:22', '2017-12-04 00:19:18', null, '5f8f4f86-602a-4d0c-b02c-abb74b9f3eaf', '1539744862658.jfif');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('bad70d74-512c-496e-87f8-32d72de2abb3', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', '0c68a514-51cd-4eba-a57c-50dd0a1e38d4', null, null, '2017年天津大学粤港澳校友联谊会在深举行', '', '<p>							</p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\"><strong>扎根粤港澳，共圆天大梦</strong></span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;text-align: center;text-indent: 36px\"><strong>----2017年天津大学粤港澳校友联谊会在深举行</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 36px\"><strong>本站讯</strong>&nbsp;2017<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">年</span>11<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">月</span>5<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">日，一年一度的天津大学粤港澳校友联谊会在深圳香蜜湖好世界国宴厅举行，约</span>500<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">名校友参加了这一年度盛会。本次大会由深圳市天津大学校友会主办，深圳市天津大学校友会</span>IT<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">分会、</span>EMBA<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">分会、建筑分会、女子分会协办。</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 36px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">当主持人宣布大会开始后，</span>4<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">位英俊潇洒的校友手执校旗庄严地迈入会场，与会人员目送校旗入场。</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">学校领导和校友会负责人依次走过红色地毯，走上主席台后与校旗合影后，全体人员起立奏唱国歌。</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;text-align: center;text-indent: 36px\"><img alt=\"\" width=\"448\" height=\"336\" src=\"http://www.tju.edu.cn/xyh/xwzx/zhxw/201711/W020171114556993473086.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;text-align: center;text-indent: 26px\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;font-family: 宋体\">大会合影</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">天津大学校长助理刘宁、校友总会秘书长潘峰、副秘书长胡如光到会祝贺。刘宁在致辞中表示：母校的发展，既是母校师生员工艰苦奋斗的结果，也是校友们在校期间积淀的优良校风和走向社会后对学校发展建设有形和无形的贡献。校友和母校荣辱与共，校友是母校声誉的缔造者，是母校精神文化和社会影响的传播者，也是学校发展建设的重要支持力量。他通报了钟登华校长当选为十九大中央候补委员，说这是我们天津大学历史上的首次，也是天津大学的光荣。同时，他还介绍了学校对“双一流”建设的规划、天津大学倡导的新工科发展思路即“天大行动”、学校人才引进、校园建设等事项，并殷切希望粤港澳三地校友会，能够继续充分利用母校和校友及校友企业的资源优势，在人才培养、科学研究、服务深圳及粤港澳大湾区经济建设等方面加强合作交流，实现互利双赢。</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;text-align: center\"><img alt=\"\" width=\"389\" height=\"292\" src=\"http://www.tju.edu.cn/xyh/xwzx/zhxw/201711/W020171114556993476909.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;font-family: 宋体\">刘宁讲话</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">深圳市天津大学校友会会长张华农在致辞中感谢母校对深圳校友会长期以来的支持和关怀，并表示我们都是天大校友，要为天大继续做贡献。表示在今后的校友会工作中，将严格遵守校友会章程，认真履行职责，以沟通为核心，以感情为纽带，以服务为平台，以事业为目标，团结理事会成员和校友，开拓进取，竭尽所能，加强校友与母校之间、校友与校友之间的联系，为校友的发展服务，为母校的发展服务，为深圳及粤港澳大湾区的建设服务，不辜负母校和校友们的殷切期望。</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;text-align: center\"><img alt=\"\" width=\"397\" height=\"298\" src=\"http://www.tju.edu.cn/xyh/xwzx/zhxw/201711/W020171114556993485901.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;font-family: 宋体\">张华农讲话</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">天津大学校友总会副会长、深圳市天津大学校友会荣誉会长曹嘉庚在致辞中指出，新一届校友会班子更加规范、更加年轻、更加朝气蓬勃，他希望校友会做好“三个服务”：为校友服务，为地方和国家的社会发展经济服务，为母校建设世界一流大学服务！</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;text-align: center\"><img alt=\"\" width=\"407\" height=\"305\" src=\"http://www.tju.edu.cn/xyh/xwzx/zhxw/201711/W020171114556993489794.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;font-family: 宋体\">曹嘉庚讲话</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 36px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">深圳市天津大学校友会秘书长倪志刚代表校友会做工作报告。报告回顾总结了深圳市天津大学校友会成立过程。目前，深圳市天津大学校友会已在理事队伍中组建了会员发展委员会、资金发展委员会、活动组织委员会、校企合作委员会、公共关系委员会等，同时计划和已经发展和增设了金融分会、</span>MBA<span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">分会、女子分会、北洋艺术分会等分支机构，并有针对性的开展相关系列活动。倪志刚还介绍了一年来开展的多项活动如校友企业走访、好项目路演等，并计划未来将增加迎新工作、成功校友拜访，走访更多校友企业，争取将深圳校友会发展成与深圳地位相匹配的优秀校友会。</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;text-align: center\"><img alt=\"微信图片_20171108135810\" width=\"454\" height=\"319\" src=\"http://www.tju.edu.cn/xyh/xwzx/zhxw/201711/W020171114556993491634.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px;font-family: 宋体\">王有忠、曹家庚、张华农三任会长共聚盛会</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: 宋体, arial;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;text-indent: 36px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体\">联谊会前后，还举行了校友对话、校友好项目、部分理事座谈会，正在筹建的深圳天津大学北洋艺术分会还带来了精彩的文艺演出。</span></p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n							</p>', null, '2018-10-17 10:55:05', '2017-12-04 00:15:33', null, '5f8f4f86-602a-4d0c-b02c-abb74b9f3eaf', '1539744905247.jpg');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('c3b5997c-13d4-4ed7-9154-7bc90b320527', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', '799c1cdb-8b0b-4c4d-a210-cd7fcb51cd25', null, null, 'About us', 'Founded in 2001, creating a study in Tianjin is to achieve China students studying in France the idea of offering students to apply for school service.', '<p>							</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>Study abroad service is concerned with the growth of people</p><p>Founded in 2001, creating a study in Tianjin is to achieve China students studying in France the idea of offering students to apply for school service. And the information about learning / research programs is crucial: Chinese students need to know what schools are suitable for themselves and how to apply for these schools. Therefore, we have set up such a platform to help Chinese students achieve this.</p><p>But a reasonable study plan is only the beginning. Chinese students need to think about future career plans. They need to discover the relationship between future career plans and learning / research programs. They need to state the above plan, to successfully obtain a student visa to france. They need to carry out the best analysis of this reasonable statement. The visa service in Tianjin can do all this. &nbsp;Learn more about how we can help you.</p><p>Now, studying in Tianjin, set up an office in Beijing and Shanghai, you can study in Tianjin by the school and visa service to get help.</p><p>Interested in more information about French schools and visas? Now begin to contact Tianjin.</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n							</p>', null, '2018-10-17 10:55:42', '2017-08-07 14:03:25', null, 'e67a2792-3819-41f9-92d3-bfa5f8e79d70', '1539744942562.jfif');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('c80d9f7a-a983-402b-a517-0e36b5c3c2eb', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', '1bf594bb-1533-47db-885a-aa8b31620b6b', null, null, '医疗首选', '', '<p>							</p><p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, simsun, Helvetica, Arial; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">医疗首选</span></span></p><p>\r\n							</p>', null, '2018-10-17 11:00:29', '2017-12-01 09:28:58', null, '5f8f4f86-602a-4d0c-b02c-abb74b9f3eaf', '1539745229172.jpg');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('c8d1612a-a7b7-4dcf-ad00-dd7ffaec4fb4', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', '799c1cdb-8b0b-4c4d-a210-cd7fcb51cd24', null, null, '10 things you\'ll never know without going abroad!', 'A lot of people go abroad, found that before going abroad cramming planning, complete loss of function. The reason for this phenomenon is largely due to the wrong cognition of life abroad.', '<p>							</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>A lot of people go abroad, found that before going abroad cramming planning, complete loss of function. The reason for this phenomenon is largely due to the wrong cognition of life abroad. When you are in the country, you will imagine what life is like after going abroad, but there are some things that you know only when you are out of the country.</p><p>1, to study English is not the master</p><p>Before I went abroad, I thought that when I got abroad, I had English environment, and I would pass the language without effort. However, in addition to children, adults to eliminate the language barrier easier said than done? No wonder many old overseas Chinese who live abroad for half a lifetime still have an elementary level of english.</p><p>2, from China food exports overseas, is for Chinese food</p><p>At home, often see such propaganda: &quot;certain&quot; traditional food exported to the world&#39;s five continents, by the people of all countries love. In fact, Chinese most foods only are in the Chinese supermarket, is in Chinese sales target, who occasionally in the restaurant a sumptuous meal, usually almost do not buy food China.</p><p>3, abroad completely out of the Chinese circle, is unlikely</p><p>Domestic people have some kind of misunderstanding: when abroad, make foreign friends, contact the western food is Western-style food...... In fact, apart from the few Chinese cities and towns, as well as living on campus, or marrying foreigners, in the big cities of the center, you live a large part in the Chinese community.</p><p>4, frequently change the occupation identity, not what great</p><p>I have no ten careers, from fast food restaurants to casino operators, from Chinese teachers to telephone salesmen, from morning paper to pizza delivery, from assembly line workers to corporate staff...... Frequent identity change, and a variety of professional attributes, is not a thing to be proud of, can only make people feel that you lack a sense of responsibility and concentration.</p><p>, 5 cars, not miles away.</p><p>Domestic press frequently reported in the past certain &quot;overseas patriots&quot; to give up the good life abroad, give up the car house, and resolutely returned to China and so on. Originally, in foreign countries, real estate, car prices are much cheaper than domestic, even if you are a general income crowd, car villa also has a share.</p><p>6, on television newspapers, not what great</p><p>In foreign countries, newspapers and television are private enterprises, so the news media here, you see, you may not be careful, you become a focal point.</p><p>7, dental care can&#39;t be ignored</p><p>In the country, when the toothache, just go to the dentist, usually do not care, many people are useful teeth bite open beer bottle cap heroic feat&quot;. Out of the country found their a white teeth, like a row of beads Saiyu Bay, we really are inferior by comparison, &quot;awkward&quot;, so take the effort to let the next generation must take good care of their own facade&quot;. Dentists are also high income, high-quality occupations abroad.</p><p>8, Western leaders not mysterious</p><p>On some occasions it is not difficult to shake hands with the mayor, provincial governor and member of parliament.</p><p>9, and their interaction is not so easy to imagine.</p><p>Domestic people think we have some foreign friends, in fact, with the Tutsi deeper level exchanges, in addition to language differences, the more important cultural barriers. Who cares about the extent of the side business to Outland, ordinary Westerners keen Chinese culture, eager to make Chinese friends less and less, &quot;Like attracts like., Birds of a feather flock together. where all the same.&quot;. But with the development of China&#39;s foreign trade and the power of the country, more and more westerners are interested in China. It is very helpful to get involved in their circle and overcome the psychological barriers of shyness.</p><p>10, highly educated intellectuals, do ordinary work is not fresh</p><p>&quot;Dragon in the shallows, scholars, Kochi do blue collar in foreign It is quite common for doctor of philosophy I have seen in India, a taxi driver, Eastern European musicians dry decoration, China computer engineer working as the meat producer. In order to survive, to a lot of time learning can take temporary setbacks, can not eat, but not ordinary, life is good!</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>\r\n							</p>', null, '2018-10-17 11:02:19', '2017-08-07 13:53:08', null, 'e67a2792-3819-41f9-92d3-bfa5f8e79d70', '1539745339933.jpg');
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES ('cae2164a-3189-4283-a512-01986962eac9', 'e53a949b-4e2e-43bb-adbc-66b07a14e0f7', '77c3cf61-dffd-4289-8d35-c07d5ff305c3', null, null, '假日', '', '<p>							</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">1月份</span><br/>　　1月1日&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%85%83%E6%97%A6\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">元旦</a>（放假三天）</p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">2月份</span><br/>　　2月15日&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD12%E4%BA%BF%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%97%A5\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">中国12亿人口日</a></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">3 月份</span><br/>　　3月5日&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E5%BF%97%E6%84%BF%E8%80%85%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E6%97%A5\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">中国青年志愿者服务日</a><br/>　　3月8日&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%9B%BD%E9%99%85%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8%E5%A6%87%E5%A5%B3%E8%8A%82\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">国际劳动妇女节</a><br/>　　3月12日<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%A4%8D%E6%A0%91%E8%8A%82\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">中国植树节</a><br/>　　3月15日&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%B6%88%E8%B4%B9%E8%80%85%E6%9D%83%E7%9B%8A%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E6%97%A5\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">消费者权益保护日</a><br/>　　3月16日&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%89%8B%E6%8B%89%E6%89%8B%E6%83%85%E7%B3%BB%E8%B4%AB%E5%9B%B0%E5%B0%8F%E4%BC%99%E4%BC%B4%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E7%BB%9F%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%8C%E5%8A%A8%E6%97%A5\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">手拉手情系贫困小伙伴全国统一行动日</a><br/>　　3月18日&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%85%A8%E5%9B